NUMBER 528
NAME Inner Sea, gulls
MONSTER_GROUP 13
PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The shrieks and squawks of hunting gulls dominate the beach at this point. Gazing out over the water one can see the large birds diving gracefully into the water, and more times than not, emerging with a fish hopelessly twitching, trapped within its 
mouth.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 529
EXIT E 527
