*DESCRIPTION_START
Probably the result of some mage with too much free time, these creatures
combine the most deadly attributes of hawks and bears.  The head is of a
hawk and the most of the rest of the creature is bearlike.  It stands over
seven feet tall and looks a bit irate.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; Text outputs
TEX1 A hawkbeast cries out in anger.
TEX2 For a brief moment, the beast's eyes turn a glowing violet.
TEXZ The hawkbeast gazes at %s, contemplating its next meal.
TEXD collapses and a violet mist exits the body and streaks upward.
TEXR Clutching wounds, the hawkbeast struggles to leave.
TEXA A hawkbeast rushes for
TEXM A hawkbeast lumbers
TEXE You hear a shrill cry far too close to you.
