Number 1411
Name Small Room with Table
REGION 204
CHANNEL 2041
DEEPCAVE
; MONSTER_GROUP 88
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small, square room has a couple torch brackets on the walls and a small
table sits between them.  The only obvious means of egress is the hallway
that goes east.  Above you, the ceiling is hidden in shadows and cobwebs.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 1412
ITEM 0 91 ADJ1=294
;
Number 1412
Name T-Shaped Hallway
REGION 204
CHANNEL 2041
DEEPCAVE
; MONSTER_GROUP 88
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small section of hallway is between three rooms.  The south end ends in
a door while the east and west ends open directly into small rooms.  Wooden
braces along the walls and overhead seem to be mere symbolic supports to
hold up the thousands of tons of rock over your head.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 1411
EXIT E 1413
ITEM 0 65 VAL2=1414 CLOSED LOCKED
IFTOUCH -1
	RANDOM DUMMY1 1 50 0
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
		DAMAGEPLR SLASH 20 You see something out of the corner of your eye and feel a burning
		ECHO PLAYER sensation and notice an arrow imbedded in you.
		ECHO OTHERS %N gazes at an arrow imbedded in %i.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
		DAMAGEPLR SLASH 20 You see something out of the corner of your eye and feel a burning
		ECHO PLAYER sensation and notice an arrow imbedded in you.
		ECHO OTHERS %N gazes at an arrow imbedded in %i.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
		DAMAGEPLR SLASH 20 You see something out of the corner of your eye and feel a burning
		ECHO PLAYER sensation and notice an arrow imbedded in you.
		ECHO OTHERS %N gazes at an arrow imbedded in %i.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
		DAMAGEPLR SLASH 20 You see something out of the corner of your eye and feel a burning
		DAMAGEPLR POISON 10 sensation and notice an arrow imbedded in you.
		ECHO OTHERS %N gazes at an arrow imbedded in %i.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
		DAMAGEALL POISON 10 A small puff of green dust is blown throughout the room.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
