Number 1413
Name Small Rectangular Room
REGION 204
CHANNEL 2041
DEEPCAVE
; MONSTER_GROUP 88
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room seems to be some sort of storeroom.  In the southeast, crates are
stacked rather high.  A roughly crafted ceiling is about ten feet from the
floor.  The floors are finished with squarish slate tiles filled with mortar.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 1412
;
Number 1414
Name Long, Narrow Room
REGION 204
CHANNEL 2041
DEEPCAVE
MONSTER_GROUP 88
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Long on the east to west side, this room looks to be some sort of meeting
hall, with a long table in the middle of it.  The table looks to be well
used but has no chairs around it.  A door is in the north wall, directly
opposite the hallway that opens up to the south.  Those are the only apparent
means of egress.
*DESCRIPTION_END
