Number 1419
Name Underground River
REGION 204
CHANNEL 2042
SUBMERGED
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in a small, but turbulent, underground river.  You rush downstream,
carried away by the current.
*DESCRIPTION_END
